  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: 1.6.7-stable\r\nOS & Version: OSX 10.12.6 / Docker 17.06 / Alpine Linux 3.5.2\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nCurl commands executed outside the container produce the same result as curl commands inside the container.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nSome commands behave the same but not all commands.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n- Start a private ethereum n/w inside docker with ports mapped to the host. Start mining.\r\n- Attach to the shell in the container\r\n- issue a curl command\r\n- Detach and issue the same curl command\r\n- compare results\r\n\r\n#### Example 1\r\n\r\n````\r\n$ docker exec -it fc91cee71783 /bin/ash\r\n/go # curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_accounts\",\"params\":[],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":[\"0x1b3f349a7186ea1abab08ffd04bd9cf2ee6fb13e\"]}\r\n/go\r\n$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_accounts\",\"params\":[],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":[\"0x1b3f349a7186ea1abab08ffd04bd9cf2ee6fb13e\"]}\r\n````\r\nObserve that the result is the same in both cases.\r\n\r\n#### Example 2\r\n\r\n````\r\n$ docker exec -it fc91cee71783 /bin/ash\r\n/go # curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0x1b3f349a7186ea1abab08ffd04bd9cf2ee6fb13e\",\"late\r\nst\"],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0x2052a187ee9ea900000\"}\r\n/go \r\n$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0x1b3f349a7186ea1afd04bd9cf2ee6fb13e\",\"latest\"],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0x0\"}\r\n````\r\nObserve that the result when outside the container returns a balance of zero while inside the container the correct balance is returned.\r\n",
